OK, Cyber Claw, Drillbit, Starscream, are now standing at the 
entrance of THE PACK base.(Destructor's base)  KitKat has asked 
Drillbit to take Cyber Claw on a tour untill Aracnia arrived.  KitKat 
and Destructor are talking about the devise and what his spies have 
dug up.  Starscream is left to guard sentry until Black Aracnia 
arrives.


::KitKat::

She looked at Starscream, "I will need you, my friend, to look out 
and keep an eye out.  Just in case other bots arrive. I am expecting 
only Aracnia to arrive here. But if anything else other than just the 
arrival of Aracnia, notify me immedeately.  When Aracnia 
arrives,please notify me right away. Thank you my friend, you have 
truely been most helpfull."

She then turned and walked with Destructor.
